snippet.title: Disney's Extreme Skate Adventure (GBA) Unedited Footage
snippet.description:
This is unedited footage from Disney's Extreme Skate Adventure for Game Boy Advance. This was captured using a Game Boy Player for GameCube and Elgato Video Capture.

Game rated E for Everyone by the ESRB.
